<sent type="title" lang="chi" page="01a" n="1">詩經諺解 卷之十五</sent>
<sent type="title3" lang="chi" page="01a" n="2">都人士之什</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="3">彼都人士ᅵ여 狐裘黃黃이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="3">뎌 都앳 人士ᅵ여 狐裘ᅵ 黃黃도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="4">其容不改며 出言有章니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="4">그 容이 改티 아니며 言을 出홈애 章이 이시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="5">行歸于周ᅵ어든 萬民所望이러니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="5">周애 行歸거든 萬民의 望던 배러니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="1">彼都人士ᅵ여 臺笠緇撮이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="1">뎌 都앳 人士ᅵ여 臺로  笠이며 緇로  撮이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="2">彼君子女여 綢直如髮이로다</sent><!--‘이로다’는 다소 불명확함-->
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="2">뎌 君子의 女여 綢直홈이 髮 도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="3">我不見兮라 我心不說호라</sent><!--‘호라’의 ‘라’는 불명확함-->
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="3">내 보디 몯혼디라 내 에 說티 아니호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b-02a" n="4">彼都人士ᅵ여 充耳琇實이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b-02a" n="4">뎌 都앳 人士ᅵ여 充耳 琇로 實엿도다</sent><!--로 ^ 實-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="1">彼君子女여 謂之尹吉이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="1">뎌 君子의 女여 尹吉이라 니놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="2">我不見兮라 我心苑結호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="2">내 보디 몯혼디라 내 애 苑結호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="3">彼都人士ᅵ여 垂帶而厲ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="3">뎌 都앳 人士ᅵ여 帶 垂홈이 厲도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="4">彼君子女여 卷髮如蠆로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="4">뎌 君子의 女여 卷 髮이 蠆 도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="5">我不見兮호니 言從之邁호리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="5">내 보디 몯호니 조차 邁호리라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="1">匪伊垂之라 帶則有餘ᅵ며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="1">垂 주리 아니라 帶 곧 餘홈이 이시며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="2">匪伊卷之라 髮則有旟ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="2">卷 주리 아니라 髮이 곧 旟홈이 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="3">我不見兮호니 云何盱矣오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="3">내 보디 몯호니 엇디 盱려뇨</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="02b" n="4">都人士 五章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b-03a" n="5">終朝采祿을 不盈一匊호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b-03a" n="5">朝ᅵ 終토록 綠을 采홈을  匊에도 盈케 몯호라</sent><!--에^도-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="1">予髮曲局니 薄言歸沐호리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="1">내의 髮이 曲局니 잠 歸야 沐호리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="2">終朝采藍을 不盈一襜호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="2">朝ᅵ 終토록 藍을 采홈을  襜의도 盈케 몯호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="3">五日爲期호니 六日不詹호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="3">五日에 期호니 六日이도록 詹티 몯호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a-03b" n="4">之子于狩댄 言韔其弓며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a-03b" n="4">之子ᅵ 가 狩홀딘댄 그 弓을 韔며</sent><!--^며-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="1">之子于釣댄 言綸之繩호리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="1">之子ᅵ 가 釣홀딘댄 蠅을 綸호리라</sent><!--‘蠅’은 원문에 ‘繩’으로 표기됨-->
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="2">其釣維何오 維魴及鱮ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="2">그 釣 거시 므스것고 魴과 밋 鱮ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="3">維魴及鱮여 薄言觀者ᅵ로리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="3">魴과 밋 鱮ᅵ여 잠간 觀호리라</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="03b" n="4">采綠 四章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="1">芃芃黍苗 陰雨膏之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="1">芃芃 黍苗 陰雨ᅵ 膏놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="2">悠悠南行을 召伯勞之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="2">悠悠 南行을 召伯이 勞놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="3">我任我輦이며 我車我牛ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="3">우리 任을 우리 輦에 며 우리 車 우리 牛에 디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="4">我行旣集니 蓋云歸哉뎌</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="4">우리 行이 이믜 集니 歸딘뎌</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="1">我徒我御ᅵ며 我師我旅ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="1">우리 徒ᅵ며 우리 御ᅵ며 우리 師ᅵ며 우리 旅ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="2">我行旣集니 蓋云歸處ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="2">우리 行이 이믜 集니 歸야 處홀디니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="3">肅肅謝功을 召伯營之며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="3">肅肅 謝엣 功을 召伯이 營며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="4">烈烈征師를 召伯成之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="4">烈烈 征 師 召伯이 成놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="1">原隰旣平며 泉流旣淸야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="1">原隰이 이믜 平며 泉流ᅵ 이믜 淸야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="2">召伯有成니 王心則寧이샷다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="2">召伯이 成홈이 이시니 王心이 곧 寧샷다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="05a" n="3">黍苗 五章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="4">隰桑有阿니 其葉有難ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="4">隰엣 桑이 阿니 그 葉이 難도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="5">旣見君子호니 其樂如何오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="5">이믜 君子를 보니 그 즐거옴이 엇더뇨</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="1">隰桑有阿니 其葉有沃이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="1">隰엣 桑이 阿니 그 葉이 沃도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="2">旣見君子호니 云何不樂이리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="2">이믜 君子를 보니 엇디 즐겁디 아니리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="3">隰桑有阿니 其葉有幽ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="3">隰엣 桑이 阿니 그 葉이 幽도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b-06a" n="4">旣見君子호니 德音孔膠ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b-06a" n="4">이믜 君子를 보니 德音이 심히 膠도다</sent><!--膠^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="1">心乎愛矣어니 遐不謂矣리오마</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="1">心에 愛커니 엇디 謂티 아니리오마</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="2">中心藏之어니 何日忘之리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="2">中心에 藏엿거니 어 날 忘리오</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="06a" n="3">隰桑 四章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a-06b" n="4">白華菅兮어든 白茅束兮니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a-06b" n="4">白華ᅵ 管얏거든 白茅로 束니라</sent><!--束^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="1">之子之遠이라 俾我獨兮아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="1">之子ᅵ 遠혼디라 날로 여곰 獨게 냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="2">英英白雲이 露彼菅茅ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="2">英英 白雲이 뎌 管茅애 露니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="3">天步艱難이어 之子不猶ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="3">天步ᅵ 艱難거 之子ᅵ 猶티 아니놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="1">滮池北流야 浸彼稻田니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="1">滮 池ᅵ 北으로 流야 뎌 稻田에 浸니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="2">嘯歌傷懷야 念彼碩人호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="2">嘯歌야 懷 傷야 뎌 碩人을 念호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="3">樵彼桑薪야 卬烘于煁호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="3">뎌 桑薪을 樵야 내 煁에 烘호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="4">維彼碩人이여 實勞我心이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="4">뎌 碩人이여 진실로 내 을 勞케 놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="1">鼓鐘于宮이어든 聲聞于外니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="1">鐘을 宮에셔 鼔거든 聲이 外예 聞니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="2">念子懆懆ᅵ어 視我邁邁아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="2">子念홈을 懆懆히 거 나를 봄을 邁邁히 냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="3">有鶖在梁이어 有鶴在林이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="3">鶖ᅵ 梁애 잇거 鶴이 林에 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="4">維彼碩人이여 實勞我心이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="4">뎌 碩人이여 진실로 내 을 勞케 놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="1">鴛鴦在梁니 戢其左翼이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="1">鴛鴦이 梁애 이시니 그 左翼을 戢놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="2">之子無良야 二三其德이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="2">之子ᅵ 良홈이 업서 그 德을 二三으로 놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="3">有扁斯石은 履之卑兮니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="3">扁 이 石은 履니도 卑니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a-08b" n="4">之子之遠이여 俾我疧兮로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a-08b" n="4">之子의 遠홈이여 날로 여곰 疷케 놋다</sent><!--케 ^ -->

<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="08b" n="1">白華 八章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="2">緜蠻黃鳥ᅵ 止于丘阿ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="2">緜蠻 黃鳥ᅵ 丘阿의 止엿도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="3">道之云遠이니 我勞如何오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="3">道ᅵ 遠니 내 勞홈이 엇더뇨</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="4">飮之食之며 敎之誨之며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="4">飮며 食며 敎며 誨며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="5">命彼後車야 謂之載之아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="5">뎌 後車 命야 載라 니가</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="1">緜蠻黃鳥ᅵ 止于丘隅ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="1">緜蠻 黃鳥ᅵ 丘隅에 止엿도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="2">豈敢憚行이리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="2">엇디 敢히 行홈을 憚리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="3">畏不能趨ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="3">能히 趨티 몯가 畏얘니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="4">飮之食之며 敎之誨之며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="4">飮며 食며 敎며 誨며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="5">命彼後車야 謂之載之아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="5">뎌 後車 命야 載라 니가</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="1">緜蠻黃鳥ᅵ 止于丘側이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="1">緜蠻 黃鳥ᅵ 丘側에 止엿도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="2">豈敢憚行이리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="2">엇디 敢히 行홈을 憚리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="3">畏不能極이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="3">能히 極디 몯가 畏얘니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="4">飮之食之며 敎之誨之며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="4">飮며 食며 敎며 誨며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="5">命彼後車야 謂之載之아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="5">뎌 後車 命야 載라 니가</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="09b" n="6">緜蠻 三章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10a" n="1">幡幡瓠葉을 采之亨之라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10a" n="1">幡幡 瓠葉을 采야 亨디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10a" n="2">君子有酒ᅵ어 酌言嘗之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10a" n="2">君子ᅵ 酒를 둣거 酌야 嘗놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10a" n="3">有兎斯首를 炮之燔之라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10a" n="3">兎의 首를 炮며 燔디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10a" n="4">君子有酒ᅵ어 酌言獻之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10a" n="4">君子ᅵ 酒를 둣거 酌야 獻놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10b" n="1">有兎斯首를 燔之炙之라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10b" n="1">兎의 首 燔며 炙디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10b" n="2">君子有酒ᅵ어 酌言酢之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10b" n="2">君子ᅵ 酒를 둣거 酌야 酢놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10b" n="3">有兎斯首를 燔之炮之라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10b" n="3">兎의 首를 燔며 炮디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10b" n="4">君子有酒ᅵ어 酌言醻之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10b" n="4">君子ᅵ 酒를 둣거 酌야 醻놋다</sent><!--‘둣거’은 영인본상 ‘듯거’과 같이 보임-->
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="10b" n="5">瓠葉 四章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11a" n="1">漸漸之石이여 維其高矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11a" n="1">漸漸 石이여 그 高도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11a" n="2">山川悠遠니 維其勞矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11a" n="2">山川이 悠遠니 그 勞도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11a" n="3">武人東征이여 不皇朝矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11a" n="3">武人의 東征홈이여 朝도 遑티 몯놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11a" n="4">漸漸之石이여 維其卒矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11a" n="4">漸漸 石이여 그 卒도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11a" n="5">山川悠遠니 曷其沒矣오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11a" n="5">山川이 悠遠니 언제 그 沒고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11a" n="6">武人東征이여 不皇出矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11a" n="6">武人의 東征홈이여 出홈을 遑티 몯놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11b" n="1">有豕白蹢니 烝涉波矣며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11b" n="1">豕ᅵ 蹢이 白니 모다 波를 涉며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11b" n="2">月離于畢니 俾滂沱矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11b" n="2">月이 畢에 離니 여곰 滂沱케 놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="11b" n="3">武人東征이여 不皇他矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11b" n="3">武人의 東征홈이여 他를 遑티 몯놋다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="11b" n="4">漸漸之石 三章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12a" n="1">苕之華ᅵ여 芸其黃矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12a" n="1">苕의 華ᅵ여 그 黃이 芸도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12a" n="2">心之憂矣여 維其傷矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12a" n="2">心의 憂홈이여 그 傷놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12a" n="3">苕之華ᅵ여 其葉靑靑이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12a" n="3">苕의 華ᅵ여 그 葉이 靑靑도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12a" n="4">知我如此ᅵ런든 不如無生이랏다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12a" n="4">내 이  줄 아던든 生이 업슴만 디 몯닷다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12b" n="1">牂羊墳首ᅵ며 三星在罶ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12b" n="1">牂羊이 首ᅵ 墳며 三星이 罶에 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12b" n="2">人可以食이언 鮮可以飽ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12b" n="2">人이 可히  食 이언 可히  飽홈은 鮮도다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="12b" n="3">苕之華 三章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12b" n="4">何草不黃이며 何日不行이며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12b" n="4">어 草ᅵ 黃티 아니며 어 날 行티 아니며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="12b" n="5">何人不將야 經營四方이리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12b" n="5">어 사이 將야 四方에 經營티 아니리오</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="13a" n="1">何草不玄이며 何人不鰥이리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13a" n="1">어 草ᅵ 玄티 아니며 어 사이 鰥이 아니리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="13a" n="2">哀我征夫ᅵ 獨爲匪民가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13a" n="2">哀홉다 우리 征夫ᅵ 홀로 民이 아니가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="13a" n="3">匪兕匪虎ᅵ어 率彼曠野아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13a" n="3">兕 아니며 虎ᅵ 아니어 뎌 曠野애 率케 냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="13a" n="4">哀我征夫ᅵ 朝夕不暇ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13a" n="4">哀홉다 우리 征夫ᅵ 朝夕에 暇티 몯놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="13b" n="1">有芃者狐ᅵ여 率彼幽草ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13b" n="1">芃 狐ᅵ여 뎌 幽草에 率놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="13b" n="2">有棧之車ᅵ여 行彼周道ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13b" n="2">棧ᄉ 車ᅵ여 뎌 周道에 行놋다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="13b" n="3">何草不黃 四章</sent>
